name: Zoo York Road #1 34th Street 40.750451, -73.989294
description: ‘Zoo York Road’ highlights city-streets and neighborhoods of New York City that have stuck with the artist through his journey. The subject is inspired by the design concept of The Beatles’ Abbey Road album cover. The zebra crossing design became iconic through this image. This project takes this concept and becomes an exploration in the artist’s style and environment. These locations can be visited physically through latitude and longitude or virtually via NFTs that exist on the Tezos blockchain.
